query:
SELECT DISTINCT lm.subjectId, lm.userId as professorId, s.name as subjectName, COUNT(lm.id) as moduleCount
FROM learning_modules lm
INNER JOIN subjects s ON lm.subjectId = s.id
GROUP BY lm.subjectId, lm.userId, s.name;
